{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id52e9d4c7-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s2638"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2638"},"text":"§ 2638.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" New grounds in support of a civil action","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In any civil action under section 515 of the Tariff Act of 1930 in which the denial, in whole or in part, of a protest is a precondition to the commencement of a civil action in the Court of International Trade, the court, by rule, may consider any new ground in support of the civil action if such new ground—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52e9d4c8-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s2638/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" applies to the same merchandise that was the subject of the protest; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52e9d4c9-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s2638/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is related to the same administrative decision listed in section 514 of the Tariff Act of 1930 that was contested in the protest.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id52e9d4ca-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/417/tIII/s301"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–417, title III, § 301","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-10"},"text":"Oct. 10, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/1736"},"text":"94 Stat. 1736","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id52e9d4cb-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id52e9d4cc-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id52e9d4cd-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 515 of the Tariff Act of 1930, referred to in text, is classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1515"},"text":"section 1515 of Title 19","children":[],"tail":", Customs Duties."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 514 of the Tariff Act of 1930, referred to in par. (2), is classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t19/s1514"},"text":"section 1514 of Title 19","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id52e9d4ce-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 2638, acts ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-06-25/ch646"},"text":"June 25, 1948, ch. 646","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/982"},"text":"62 Stat. 982","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-06-02"},"text":"June 2, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/271/tI/s119"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–271, title I, § 119","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/281"},"text":"84 Stat. 281","children":[],"tail":", related to decisions, findings of fact and conclusions of law, and effect of opinions, prior to the general revision of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/417"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–417","children":[],"tail":". See section 2645 (a) and (c) of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
